<!DOCTYPE html>
<html>
<head>
    <meta charset="utf-8" />
    <meta http-equiv="X-UA-Compatible" content="IE=edge">
    <title>Signup</title>
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1">
    <link rel="stylesheet" href="https://stackpath.bootstrapcdn.com/bootstrap/4.1.3/css/bootstrap.min.css">
    <link rel="stylesheet" href="/css/profile.css">
</head>
<body>

<nav class="navbar navbar-expand-lg navbar-dark" style="background-color: #3B5998;">
  <div class="container">
    <a class="navbar-brand" href="/" style="color: #fff">faceblog</a>
    <div class="collapse navbar-collapse" id="navbarText">
      <div class="navbar-nav ml-auto">
        <div class="navbar-collapse collapse w-100 order-3 dual-collapse2">
          <a class="nav-item nav-link active" href="/profile">Profile <span class="sr-only">(current)</span></a>
          <a class="nav-item nav-link" href="/logout">Logout</a>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</nav>

<div class="container">
  <div class="row">
    <div class="col-8 pt-5">
    <h1>Welcome back <%= user.firstname %>! </h1>

    <p>Did you know that one of our recent surveys demonstrated that most of our users want to have a social platform that doesn't track their users?</p>
    <p>Well, this is your lucky day!</p>
    <p><strong>Faceblog</strong> is a social platform on which you can share your thoughts or interesting topics by <a href="/createpost">creating a post</a>. Keep track of your <a href="/posts">own posts</a> and posts of <a href="/allposts">other users</a>. Read, think, share and smile! Please be polite to other users when commenting on other users because we're soft as kittens and don't allow buzzy and fuzzy posts/comments on our platform.</p>
  </div>
    <div class="col-4">
      <div class="list-group pt-5">
        <a href="/settings" class="list-group-item list-group-item-action list-group-item-light">Account settings</a>
        <a href="/createpost" class="list-group-item list-group-item-action list-group-item-light">Create a new post</a>
        <a href="/posts" class="list-group-item list-group-item-action list-group-item-light">View your posts</a>
        <a href="/allposts" class="list-group-item list-group-item-action list-group-item-light">View other user's posts</a>
      </div>
    </div>
</div>
</div>

<script src="https://code.jquery.com/jquery-3.3.1.slim.min.js"></script>
<script src="https://cdnjs.cloudflare.com/ajax/libs/popper.js/1.14.3/umd/popper.min.js"></script>
<script src="https://stackpath.bootstrapcdn.com/bootstrap/4.1.3/js/bootstrap.min.js"></script>
<script type="text/javascript" src="/js/jquery.js"></script>
</body>
</html>
